<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL ROUNDUP: NATIONAL TECHNICAL BUYS FIRM FOR $1.75 MILLION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
National Technical Systems Inc. in Calabasas said it acquired Wise &amp; 
Associates Inc. of San Antonio, Tex., for $1.75 million. 
</P>
<P>
National Technical, with $30 million in revenue for its fiscal year that ended 
last Jan. 31, provides testing and engineering services. Wise, through its 
S&amp;W Technical Services unit, provides technical support mainly for the 
nuclear power industry. Its revenue for the fiscal year that ended May 31 was 
$12 million. 
</P>
</TEXT>
