Frankfurters Are Being Recalled: A Chicago food processer, David Berg &amp; 
Co., is recalling 10,000 pounds of beef frankfurters and 1,400 pounds of deli 
beef franks because they may contain a bacteria that can cause listeriosis, a 
rare but potentially fatal disease. The recall applies to bulk-packed David 
