<TEXT>
<P>
Touchstone Software Corp.: The Huntington Beach software company said 
third-quarter earnings increased to $56,652 from $3,335 for the comparable 1989 
quarter. 
</P>
<P>
Revenue rose 85%, to $741,951 from $400,494. For the nine-month period, 
earnings jumped to $121,214 from $42,986 in the year-earlier period. Revenue 
more than doubled to $2.5 million from $1.1 million. 
