<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
For Better Living Inc.: The San Juan Capistrano building-products maker and 
magazine publisher posted net income of $610,000 for the third quarter, up 75% 
from the $348,000 reported for the 1989 third quarter. 
</P>
<P>
Sales rose 6%, to $23.8 million from $22.5 million. Net income for the first 
nine months of the year totaled $945,000, 59% higher than the $596,000 posted 
for the comparable three quarters in 1989. Sales declined 4%, to $62.2 million 
from $64.5 million. 
</P>
