<TEXT>
<P>
Former Defense Minister Yitzhak Rabin told Israeli Prime Minister Yitzhak 
Shamir today to keep his mouth shut about the occupied territories so the world 
could focus on the Persian Gulf crisis. 
</P>
<P>
The 75-year-old Shamir, risking a dispute with Israel's chief ally -- the 
